Rating: 4
This one is special. A unique cross between shortbread and pound cake. Somehow it is elegant and comforting at once. Two teaspoons of vanilla works perfectly if you don't have vanilla sugar/bean, and 3/4 teaspoon of salt is sufficient if you only have unsalted butter on hand. Overall, it is dense, buttery, and just delicious.

