Rating: 4
This was an easy recipe to make. The aroma while it was baking was incredible. I used egg white wash over the top instead of the yolk. I didn't have a vanilla bean so I used 1 & 1/2 tsp. double strength extract instead. It was still very delicious. It's like a shortbread in a dense cake...a great scone replacement. I am saving this one!!

